# Tokens & Theming Rules
- Use tokens from the theme folder:
  - Colors: `theme/colors.ts` (green primary `tint`, surfaces, text, border, status)
  - Spacing: `theme/spacing.ts`
  - Typography: `theme/typography.ts`
  - Radius: `theme/radius.ts`
- Import via `constants/theme.ts` where needed, and `use-theme-color` for runtime colors.
- Never hard-code hex/rgb in components.
- One accent color only (green-ish primary). Status colors for state only.
- Implement dark mode via paired tokens; avoid inline color branching.

